    "If an account exists for that email, we've sent a password reset link. Check your inbox and spam folder.": {
      "comment": "Forgot password success body",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If an account exists for that email, we've sent a password reset link. Check your inbox and spam folder."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se existe uma conta para esse e-mail, enviamos um link de redefinição de senha. Verifique sua caixa de entrada e pasta de spam."
